 female sexuality. Illuminating the cross-pollination of black sexuality and BDSM, The Color of Kink makes a unique contribution to the growing scholarship on racialized sexuality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aBondage (Sexual behavior). 0aPornography. 0aSadomasochism. 0aWomen, BlackxSexual behavior. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Feminism & Feminist Theory.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.18574/nyu/9781479809288.001.000140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781479899425423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781479899425/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles